* Granularity\nTrade-offs
** Fine Granularity
***_ High analytical flexibility
***_ Higher storage costs
***_ Slower aggregate queries
***_ More historical detail
** Coarse Granularity
***_ Lower storage costs
***_ Faster common query patterns
***_ Limited drill-down
***_ May lose historical detail
** Resolution
***_ Atomic detail + aggregate layers
***_ Materialized views auto-maintained
***_ Balance current and future requirements
@endmindmap
